26 October 2015The Economic Sectors, Employment and Infrastructure Development Cluster (ESEID) chaired by the Minister of Rural Development and Land Reform, Gugile Nkwinti will host a media briefing to give an update on progress made by the Cluster.The media briefing will be held as follows:Date: Wednesday, 28 October 2015 Time: 08h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street in Parliament, Cape TownN.B: There with be a video link up to GCIS Head Office, 1035 Francis Baard, Tshedimosetso House, Pretoria.Kindly confirm attendance by email or sms to:Andile Duka (Cape Town) E-mail: Andiled@gcis.gov.za Cell: 071 154 5619Ireen Magwai (Pretoria) E-mail: Ireen@gcis.gov.za Cell: 082 440 5676Enquiries: David Jacobs Cell: 083 681 8904Sivuyile Mangxamba Cell: 071 334 2915 Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)